    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Rye was founded in 1660 by Thomas Studwell, Peter Disbrow, and John Coe.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        5
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rye%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Colonists may have named Rye after the English seaside town of the same name or after the Browne family’s hometown.",
